&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description></item><item><title>读书笔记</title><link>/post/2024/02/01/%E8%AF%BB%E4%B9%A6%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 16:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/2024/02/01/%E8%AF%BB%E4%B9%A6%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;读书使人充实，思考使人深邃。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>技术入门</title><link>/post/2024/01/15/%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8/</link><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 14:30:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>/post/2024/01/15/%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;技术之路，始于足下。&lt;/p&gt;
